divs: Sighting DetailsMyself(Douglas Walker)and My girlfriend Jessica were standing out back on my porch.I was looking up when I observed a bright orange light heading SW to NW.I told Jess to look up at the strange light and she said thats kind of weird.Then I went down into the yard and it was still there.She really wasnt going to think twice and disregard my lights I see.I said to her its still here and she came down and was like what is that.Definitely weird.She actually did a small drawing of what she described as triangular in shape with a core starlight in the center.She actually had a better view as she has better vision than I.I myself only made out a bright orange starlight at close distance movin slow and steady which dimmed and then disappeared in the distance.She seen a tringle shaped craft.With a star oike core emmitting a bright orange light.I did call a neighbor and they went out and looked but it dimmed once it got over there home.
